metadata.name: wonderland #01
metadata.description:
e9Art - welcome to wonderland


i believe in the power of imagination. i believe in fairy tales and happily-ever-afters.

and most importantly of all, i believe in impossible things.

this hasn’t always been the case. to quote Lewis Carroll: “When I used to read fairy tales, I fancied that kind of thing never happened, and now here I am in the middle of one!” 

yes, it’s true. i’ve swallowed the red pill. 

i’ve fallen through the rabbit hole and landed in wonderland … and it doesn’t stop there. 

the adventure has only just begun …

digital art by e9Art using disco diffusion and photoshop, May 2022
